## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of data and the scope of the sources reviewed. While the sources provide a broad overview, they may not capture all nuances of the gender pay gap across different cultures and industries. Additionally, the data is primarily from Western contexts, which may not fully represent global disparities. Further research could explore more diverse geographical and cultural perspectives to provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.

